title: Illusion Play Club Retail Download
description:
This is a retail version of Illusion's newest game Play Club with the original DLC packs.

Read the enclosed read me for English game install instructions.

I suggest you have Hongfire's custom AppLocale installed and a copy of Daemon Tools Lite prior to installation.

Read upon the install of Japanese Games is you are a first timer.

NOTE: This is an adult pornographic game focused on the concept of women that have been abducted by a rich old man who sells sexual adventures through his secret club to wealthy perverts. The main male characters explore his mansion to find the women then forcibly take sexual favors from the abducted slaves... 

You have been warned of the content - this is not a Japanese RPG suitable for a 10 year old. If you are stupid enough to proceed then do not complain here
